'''Aqua cycling''' or '''aqua spinning''' is a technique in fitness training.<ref>[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/health-fitness/fitness/Aqua-workouts/articleshow/33336550.cms "Aqua workouts"]. ''The Times of India''.</ref> In aqua cycling, a stationary apparatus similar to a bicycle frame is submerged in a pool, while its rider's upper body remains above the water.<ref>[http://www.chron.com/technology/businessinsider/article/We-Tried-Underwater-Cycling-The-Latest-Exercise-4753431.php "We Tried Underwater Cycling, The Latest Exercise Craze In New York City"]. ''Houston Chronicle''.</ref> == Private Aqua Cycling == Private Aqua Cycling is a fitness concept that combines underwater workout with active balneotherapy in private rooms.<ref>http://whatson.ae/dubai/knowledge/7914/aquabiking-in-dubai-video/</ref>
